text:
yooo it worked! turns out you have to associate the line_item with the deal through the body request when creating the line_item, something like this:

```{
  "properties": {
    "name": "Novo Produto 11:10",
    "quantity": 1,
    "hs_sku": "new_product", 
    "price": 131
  },
  "associations": [
    {
      "to": {
        "id": &lt;deal_id&gt;
      },
      "types": [
        {
          "associationCategory": "HubSpot_DEFINED",
          "associationTypeId": 20
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}```
